<p>Most explanations of Bitcoin payments stop at the theory. This one doesn't. Rachel walks me through making a real Bitcoin invoice end to end — pricing it in dollars, sending it, and watching the payment land and confirm on-chain. By the end you'll be able to do the same.</p>

